{"id":533398,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/06/【异闻观止】/","date":"2016-06-27T07:46:15Z","modified":"2016-08-17T07:17:14Z","title":"【异闻观止】网络反共反华组织曝光 或与秦火火有关","content":"<p><strong>数字时代编辑注：</strong>本文为察网中国独家投稿(www.cwzg.cn)（原站如此注明），关于此站，其首页官方简介如下：</p>\n<blockquote><p>“察网中国”是由海南察网文化传媒有限公司运营的民间性质爱国网民网站。我们的宗旨是：积极宣传党和政府的有关方针政策；维护国家利益，保卫国家安全；汇聚爱国能量，巩固爱国阵线；弘扬民族精神，传承民族文化。</p></blockquote>\n<p>昨日，一张2016年5月的《舆情员津贴奖金发放表》曝光，其中显示“舆情员”所领津贴奖金数目惊人，其中“梅雪飘香”即为该组织头目，也为该表统计人。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533401\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627122247507.png\" alt=\"20160627122247507\" width=\"550\" height=\"395\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627122247507.png 582w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627122247507-300x215.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-533402\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123331157.png\" alt=\"20160627123331157\" width=\"490\" height=\"462\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123331157.png 490w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123331157-300x283.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px\" /></p>\n<p>这个33人的团队，仅2016年5月份的舆情员津贴奖金就高达近27万元，其平均每人每月高达8000多元。而且此表注明<strong>【单位：部直属第5分队】</strong>，说明这只是整个组织中的一小支分队。整个组织有多么庞大，其资金规模投入有多大？细想恐怖至极。</p>\n<p>一、该组织主要头目“梅雪飘香”的基本情况</p>\n<p>仔细分析研究，这是一股早已在网络上存在多年的有组织化地反共反华网络水军。其头目“梅雪飘香”的博客地址为：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/u/1247372933\">http://blog.sina.com.cn/u/1247372933</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/meixuepiaoxiang1107\">http://blog.sina.com.cn/meixuepiaoxiang1107</a></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-533405\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123402268.png\" alt=\"20160627123402268\" width=\"231\" height=\"790\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123402268.png 231w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123402268-88x300.png 88w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 231px) 100vw, 231px\" /></p>\n<p>图表显示，此人2016年5月通过支付宝领取反共反华势力发放的舆情员津贴奖金10560元！！</p>\n<p>其对应的微博名原为“梅雪飘香1107”“梅雪飘香-1107”等都以被封杀，但从遗留的信息看此人多年在网络上进行反共反华活动，且曾经与秦火火团伙有一定关系：</p>\n<p><strong>1、梅雪飘香在新浪博客及微博上发表秦火火制造的相关文章：</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-533406\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123428553.png\" alt=\"20160627123428553\" width=\"554\" height=\"168\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123428553.png 554w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123428553-300x91.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 554px) 100vw, 554px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533407\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123438710.png\" alt=\"20160627123438710\" width=\"550\" height=\"222\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123438710.png 651w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123438710-300x121.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2、梅雪飘香在博客上推广恶毒造谣攻击毛泽东的文章：</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533408\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123456635.png\" alt=\"20160627123456635\" width=\"550\" height=\"122\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123456635.png 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123456635-300x67.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>3、梅雪飘香吹捧美国驻华大使并积极帮助美国在华进行舆论政治渗透的活动</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-533411\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123519774.png\" alt=\"20160627123519774\" width=\"550\" height=\"226\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123519774.png 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123519774-300x123.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533412\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123538394.png\" alt=\"20160627123538394\" width=\"550\" height=\"102\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123538394.png 636w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123538394-300x56.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>4、梅雪飘香恶毒攻击中国社会和政治制度，煽动颜色革命的微博</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533413\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123552774.png\" alt=\"20160627123552774\" width=\"550\" height=\"160\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123552774.png 650w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123552774-300x87.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533414\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123609214.png\" alt=\"20160627123609214\" width=\"550\" height=\"199\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123609214.png 480w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123609214-300x109.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>5、梅雪飘香在博客上传播造谣攻击十月革命及共产主义运动的文章：</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-533415\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123643446.png\" alt=\"20160627123643446\" width=\"477\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123643446.png 477w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123643446-300x252.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 477px) 100vw, 477px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>6、梅雪飘香力挺被捕的亲美亲日极端公知信力建：</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-533416\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123706389.png\" alt=\"20160627123706389\" width=\"556\" height=\"322\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123706389.png 556w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123706389-300x174.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 556px) 100vw, 556px\" /></p>\n<p>了解了这个组织的主要头目，这个组织的政治性质和倾向也就比较清楚了。</p>\n<p><strong>二、该组织另一位主要成员二级成员“活雷锋啊小东”</strong></p>\n<p>另外，从其主要成员的情况看，这个组织属于反共反华公知组织确定无疑：</p>\n<p>在《舆情员津贴奖金发放表》中，有一个仅次于梅雪飘香的二级成员，其网络id为“活雷锋啊小东”，图表显示其2016年5月领取反共反华势力发放的津贴为8750元！！</p>\n<p>我们看下其腾讯微博的内容，可以发现，这是一个典型的反共反华公知：</p>\n<p><strong>“活雷锋啊小东”恶毒攻击党和国家领导人及社会制度：</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533417\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123741447.png\" alt=\"20160627123741447\" width=\"550\" height=\"177\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123741447.png 596w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123741447-300x97.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-533420\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123800213.png\" alt=\"20160627123800213\" width=\"554\" height=\"247\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123800213.png 554w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123800213-300x134.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 554px) 100vw, 554px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533419\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627033801637.jpg\" alt=\"20160627033801637\" width=\"550\" height=\"457\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627033801637.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627033801637-300x249.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>“活雷锋啊小东”恶毒攻击司马南及罗援的东西，和秦火火一模一样，<strong>这再一次证明这个组织与秦火火的关系密切，当年只抓了一个秦火火，却留下了整个网络反共水军： </strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533422\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627033815983.jpg\" alt=\"20160627033815983\" width=\"550\" height=\"248\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627033815983.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627033815983-300x135.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>《舆情员津贴奖金发放表》曝光后，该组织成员试图藏匿。“活雷锋啊小东”的腾讯微博虽然改名，不过还是被笔者活捉了：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-533423\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123833573.png\" alt=\"20160627123833573\" width=\"555\" height=\"102\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123833573.png 555w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123833573-300x55.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 555px) 100vw, 555px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-533424\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123856103.png\" alt=\"20160627123856103\" width=\"558\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123856103.png 558w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123856103-300x150.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 558px) 100vw, 558px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-533425\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124313876.png\" alt=\"20160627124313876\" width=\"555\" height=\"374\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124313876.png 555w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124313876-300x202.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 555px) 100vw, 555px\" /></p>\n<p>此人腾讯微博现改名为“蒙J&#8212;魏志强”，并自我介绍为“本人铁杆汉奸！”，而之前的微博介绍是“望认同普世价值的博友互粉”。这个事实又一次雄辩地证明：普世价值派即铁杆汉奸！！</p>\n<p>此人腾讯微博也是清一色的反共反华内容：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533426\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123918266.png\" alt=\"20160627123918266\" width=\"550\" height=\"570\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123918266.png 658w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627123918266-289x300.png 289w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533427\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124028173.png\" alt=\"20160627124028173\" width=\"550\" height=\"727\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124028173.png 636w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124028173-227x300.png 227w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>三、从该组织成员二级成员“张激扬”的基本情况分析该组织基本动向</strong></p>\n<p>最后我们再介绍一位《舆情员津贴奖金发放表》中的二级成员“张激扬”，其2016年5月份领取的金额为8650元。</p>\n<p>“张激扬”腾讯微博及相关反共反华内容：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533428\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124356989.png\" alt=\"20160627124356989\" width=\"550\" height=\"580\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124356989.png 591w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124356989-285x300.png 285w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533429\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124418950.png\" alt=\"20160627124418950\" width=\"550\" height=\"428\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124418950.png 638w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124418950-300x233.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>此人的新浪微博，也证明此人是典型的反共反华公知，其粉丝仅有671人：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-533430\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124442849.png\" alt=\"20160627124442849\" width=\"520\" height=\"419\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124442849.png 520w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124442849-300x242.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 520px) 100vw, 520px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-533431\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124505159.png\" alt=\"20160627124505159\" width=\"523\" height=\"562\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124505159.png 523w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124505159-279x300.png 279w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 523px) 100vw, 523px\" /></p>\n<p>不过非常明显的是，“张激扬”此人的智商比起同伙“活雷锋啊小东”来，要低一大截。《舆情员津贴奖金发放表》曝光后，“活雷锋啊小东”腾讯微博改名为 “蒙J&#8212;魏志强”，<strong>并将“望认同普世价值的博友互粉”自我介绍改成“本人铁杆汉奸！”，以期望逃脱惩罚，长期潜伏。</strong></p>\n<p>可笑的是，“张激扬”却故意装作镇静：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533432\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124632717.png\" alt=\"20160627124632717\" width=\"550\" height=\"465\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124632717.png 596w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124632717-300x254.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>由此我们也有机会查下公知的微博多少钱一条。此人腾讯微博14年11月以来没有更新，其新浪微博2016年5月仅发了两条原创，其中一条还是上海聚会照片：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533433\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124703840.png\" alt=\"20160627124703840\" width=\"550\" height=\"717\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124703840.png 592w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124703840-230x300.png 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>其2016年5月份所发微博主要是转发，约为30条，主要是转发一些反共反华微博大V和营销账号的煽动性、造谣性微博：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533434\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124726583.png\" alt=\"20160627124726583\" width=\"550\" height=\"693\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124726583.png 586w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124726583-238x300.png 238w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533435\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124805818.png\" alt=\"20160627124805818\" width=\"550\" height=\"437\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124805818.png 587w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124805818-300x238.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533436\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124823937.png\" alt=\"20160627124823937\" width=\"550\" height=\"658\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124823937.png 528w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124823937-251x300.png 251w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533437\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124935118.png\" alt=\"20160627124935118\" width=\"550\" height=\"705\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124935118.png 590w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627124935118-234x300.png 234w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>百度搜索显示，除了腾讯微博和新浪微博，此人并无其他的公开网络活动平台：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-533438\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627125023104.png\" alt=\"20160627125023104\" width=\"550\" height=\"424\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627125023104.png 612w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627125023104-300x231.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>根据《舆情员津贴奖金发放表》，<strong>二级成员“张激扬”2016年5月份领取的金额为8650元，其微博工作主要是转发了30条微博</strong>，而其新浪微博粉丝仅为671人。这种异常情况只能说明，这不是一个普通的网络水军组织，如果其反共反华活动主要在网络的话，其主要活动平台推测在更为隐蔽的微信上。</p>\n<p>该组织头目“梅雪飘香”在2015年9月9日发了这样一篇博文，显示微信已经是其主要战场：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-533439\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627125105601.png\" alt=\"20160627125105601\" width=\"517\" height=\"432\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627125105601.png 517w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/06/20160627125105601-300x251.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 517px) 100vw, 517px\" /></p>\n<p>笔者能做的，只有这些了。更多的不为人知的黑幕有待专业机构更进一步的调查。</p>\n","author":1003,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20505],"tags":[21903,14541,22957,11741,26048,17029,27862,24128,19248,15372,31597,15287]}